 ${userId} not found for sync`);\n    return false;\n  }\n\n  // In a real app, we'd sync to an external service here\n  console.log(`Synced user ${user.name} (${user.email})`);\n  return true;\n}\n","structuredPatch":[{"oldStart":4,"oldLines":7,"newStart":4,"newLines":7,"lines":["  */"," "," import {","-  createUser,","+  registerUser,","   getUserById,","   getAllUsers,","   type CreateUserInput,"]}],"userModified":false,"replaceAll":false}}
